| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1319 — Recovery Inhibition (cicada3301)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 593e2aa5-f810-53c6-9c8d-44f9b360d1b3"
